322
00:21:28,920 --> 00:21:29,480
Right.

323
00:21:30,680 --> 00:21:32,240
Let's send him down!

324
00:21:33,680 --> 00:21:34,400
Okay.

325
00:22:09,750 --> 00:22:10,510
Sheng!

326
00:22:23,070 --> 00:22:23,880
Senior,

327
00:22:24,240 --> 00:22:25,000
