328
00:22:27,510 --> 00:22:28,270
Sheng!

329
00:22:30,640 --> 00:22:31,640
Sheng!

330
00:22:41,720 --> 00:22:42,400
Sheng.

331
00:22:42,790 --> 00:22:43,400
Sheng!

332
00:22:45,070 --> 00:22:45,790
Senior,

333
00:22:46,110 --> 00:22:46,680
