391
00:25:44,830 --> 00:25:45,510
Sheng.

392
00:25:46,790 --> 00:25:47,720
Don't cry.

393
00:25:48,960 --> 00:25:50,920
Don't cry, Senior.

394
00:25:52,550 --> 00:25:53,480
Senior.

395
00:25:55,590 --> 00:25:56,640
I really,

396
00:25:58,240 --> 00:26:00,240
