443
00:28:10,200 --> 00:28:10,920
Senior.

444
00:28:11,680 --> 00:28:13,340
Let's go back to Xin Xie Manor.

445
00:28:13,480 --> 00:28:14,640
I want to go home.

446
00:28:15,720 --> 00:28:17,590
The fish we raised in the pond last year

447
00:28:17,590 --> 00:28:18,850
