455
00:28:55,350 --> 00:28:56,000
Master,

456
00:28:56,640 --> 00:28:57,350
Junior,

457
00:28:58,440 --> 00:28:59,500
fellow disciples,

458
00:28:59,790 --> 00:29:01,030
