527
00:34:49,840 --> 00:34:50,710
Fine.

528
00:34:51,810 --> 00:34:54,190
You had a chance to live,
yet you refused it.

529
00:34:54,190 --> 00:34:55,790
Since you're so eager to die,

530
00:34:56,480 --> 00:34:57,680
