576
00:37:27,360 --> 00:37:29,610
♪ I ask the Nine Heavens:
what is the purpose of this life? ♪

577
00:37:29,640 --> 00:37:32,430
♪ With my spine as my monument,
I shall never kneel ♪

578
00:37:33,400 --> 00:37:35,500
